{"tid":313473,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"手機將變Gameboy　今年暑假正式發售","createTime":"2017-07-08T11:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T03:13:34.000Z","uid":58099,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6be29f8e97c829aadcf30c6569819070ad5a7410","tid":313473,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T11:02:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/190016_a08316b400e56a0d54807c98667b3c49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F190016_a08316b400e56a0d54807c98667b3c49.jpg&h=42e56fab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想在手機上玩 Game Boy 遊戲，相信不少人應該會聯想起模擬器這種東西。不過若然大家本身有儲開 Game Boy 遊戲，而有想玩到帶內的儲存進度，其實亦未必一定需要用上 Game Boy 主機。因為今年暑假Hyperlink 就公開了一款 Smart Boy 配件，只需插上一部 Android 手機即可變身成一部 Game Boy，而更重要的是大家更可以插遊戲帶來玩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/190034_d0c67b082a7ecfce5195a559ff00e705.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F190034_d0c67b082a7ecfce5195a559ff00e705.jpg&h=b9749fdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這個「SmartBoy」主要對應Samsung手機，使用Android系統，用上USB 把「SmartBoy」及手機連接，並不需要用電。機面設計如同首代Gameboy一樣，十字掣、AB掣、Start和Select掣。背後提供卡帶位置，支援Gameboy及Gameboy Color的遊戲帶，任何國家版本的遊戲帶。機背按鈕供機身闊度調整，讓不同大小的機種安置，手機大小5.2至6英吋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/190051_7e7d95fd9ce1bc07b47b1aa6b0e08e1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F190051_7e7d95fd9ce1bc07b47b1aa6b0e08e1d.jpg&h=758ee248&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSmart Boy 上設有十字掣、A、B、Start 及 Select 掣，在上面插上一部 Android 機後即會變成一部 Game Boy。此外，Smart Boy 背後同時亦設有一個插卡槽，可以直接插入 Game Boy 或 Game Boy Color 遊戲帶來遊玩，而這項功能正正是其魅力之一。<br />\n<br />\nSmartBoy」將會透過「Samsung Mobile Accessory Partnership Program」在美國和南韓市場出售，售價為50美元。"},{"pid":"a7cf4666a0d4158b60b9ef4c973704b6a0655f4d","tid":313473,"uid":124560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T11:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83fb0947c7454ede4000b2e7eac38df7866c1db4","tid":313473,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T11:04:18.000Z","msg":"咁搞無左full screen, 真係純粹懷舊"},{"pid":"a0b1df4766bd7979a200558a9e113d43a80fc437","tid":313473,"uid":37136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T11:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c13411a4d1e4f9223c8c5a97266ced117a667d1a","tid":313473,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T11:07:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁搞無左full screen, 真係純粹懷舊</blockquote><br />\ngameboy game 支援full screen?"},{"pid":"084c7ba278a14cda8b5db25b201f34645b45768a","tid":313473,"uid":44044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T11:09:20.000Z","msg":"睇圖仲以為iphone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db2ce2f335e034bcfe0cebf53cc2b9dfce226682","tid":313473,"uid":38915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T11:23:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇圖仲以為iphone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個制圓型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c518eb62e14e6179df705be9eaa20fd76d4777f1","tid":313473,"uid":25148,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T12:02:34.000Z","msg":"概念圖用iphone但同我講for an機<br />\n唉我出返去先"},{"pid":"257caccf12d4780d25a5d59faad17f66541b4148","tid":313473,"uid":49978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T12:16:27.000Z","msg":"邊有帶"},{"pid":"12ee0b4dae07e7efb7e97336d5771e0805639a79","tid":313473,"uid":46644,"like":0,"dislike